desc:
Hello there! This site was built from the [Stello Boilerplate][sb] board, which demonstrates how to structure your Trello boards for use with *stello*. For this example we're using a public board, but private boards will work too.

For more information on *stello* see the docs on the [GitHub repo][gh].

[sb]: https://trello.com/b/u4YdciVy "Stello Boilerplate Trello board"
[gh]: https://github.com/jtrussell/stello "Stello on GitHub"
name: First Page
